            p We have the greatest facilities possible
      div.slider__slide.slider__slide--2
        div.slider__lead.bold OUR HOSPITAL
        div.slider__heading.bold Facilities
        div.slider__text.bold Services
          div
            p We offer you the best of our abilities
      div.slider__slide.slider__slide--3
        div.slider__lead.bold OUR HOSPITAL
        div.slider__heading.bold Staff
        div.slider__text.bold Professionalism
          div
            p Our team is professional with cutting-edge technology
      div.slider__slide.slider__slide--4
        div.slider__lead.bold OUR HOSPITAL
        div.slider__heading.bold Staff
        div.slider__text.bold Moments
          div
            p We care for your every moment
    
